<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٢٩⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">عَنْ عَائِشَةَ <span class="special">﵂</span> قالَتْ:</span> تُوُفِّي رَسُولُ اللهِ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> وَقَدْ شَبِعْنَا مِنَ الأَسْوَدَيْنِ: التَّمْرِ وَالْمَاءِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>